description: Sweet Daddy's BBQ is a delicious BBQ trailer serving the streets of the Royal Palm Beach area. From St. Louis-Style ribs, Smoked Brisket, Pulled Pork, Smoked Chicken, and Apple Wood Smoked Bacon, to Southern Fried Chicken and Catfish with grits and hushpuppies, to BBQ Bacon Loaf Sandwiches, Southern Potato Salad, Sweet and Tangy Coleslaw, Hog and Apple Baked Beans, Collard Greens and Baked Mac n' Cheese, Sweet Daddy's can satisfy any craving. "Put some true south in your mouth!"
name: Sweet Daddy's BBQ
